  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Strengthening the engagement of civil society in sustainable and environmental development work across Guangxi Province</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will increase awareness and support for environmental education in China by casting a light upon the achievements of groups (such as BRC) and fostering public and government support for their interventions. In the longer-term a growing awareness of environmental groups and growing public interest (and participation in) conservation work not only will lead to positive impacts on environmental and economic well-being, but may also will enhance the UK&apos;s relationship with the Guangxi government and promote UK universities to students.</narrative>
